sentences.en: The traditional owners of Uluru - Kata Tjuta are the Anangu Aboriginal people.
sentences.cn: 乌卢鲁-卡塔曲塔原来的拥有者是阿南古土著人.

sentences.en: We are ready to head off to Uluru, the artist formerly known as Ayers Rock.
sentences.cn: 我们准备去乌鲁鲁了, 艺术家们从前把它称为艾尔斯岩.

trans.tran_cn: 澳州艾尔斯岩，[地名] [澳大利亚] 乌卢鲁巨石
乌卢鲁，埃尔斯岩（Ayres Rock）的土著名
